Package: soccermatrix
Type: Package
Title: Assists in Data Gathering and Matrix Conversion
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: "Alejandro Cepeda <acepeda19@usf.edu> [aut, cre]"
Description: This package contains FBref and Transfermarkt data sets of both players and teams from all major leagues and divisions. 
    Additionally, there is a function for matrix conversion to use for visualizations such as heat maps and even certain machine learning 
    methods that require matrix form data, such as Clustering for example.The purpos of this package is to skip certain steps that are common
    when working with soccer data and allow the user to not be required to manually download the data from the mentioned sources.
Depends: R(>= 4.1.3)
License: CC0
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: no
Packaged: 2022-03-25 02:14:10 UTC; alece
Author: "Alejandro Cepeda" [aut, cre]
Maintainer: "Alejandro Cepeda" <acepeda19@usf.edu>
